WEBVTT

00:00:05.192 --> 00:00:14.368 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
How can we endure
When trials come, as Jesus said?

00:00:14.368 --> 00:00:23.294 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Through his pain he saw
The joy of better things ahead.

00:00:23.294 --> 00:00:32.928 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God’s promise, God’s justice,
Were thoughts on which he fed.

00:00:32.928 --> 00:00:42.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We need to have endurance.
Our faith we must defend.

00:00:42.229 --> 00:00:56.327 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His love is our assurance.
So we will keep enduring to the end.

00:00:56.327 --> 00:01:05.628 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Though the passing years
May bring us sorrow, bring us pain;

00:01:05.628 --> 00:01:14.720 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There beyond the tears,
We see the life that we can gain.

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:24.271 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To be there, feel free there,
Determined we remain.

00:01:24.271 --> 00:01:33.322 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We need to have endurance.
Our faith we must defend.

00:01:33.322 --> 00:01:47.670 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His love is our assurance.
So we will keep enduring to the end.

00:01:47.670 --> 00:01:56.762 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We will not give up
Nor see the need for doubt or fear.

00:01:56.762 --> 00:02:06.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Faithfully we’ll serve
Until Jehovah’s day is here.

00:02:06.063 --> 00:02:15.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s keep on enduring.
That time is very near.

00:02:15.364 --> 00:02:24.748 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We need to have endurance.
Our faith we must defend.

00:02:24.748 --> 00:02:37.177 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His love is our assurance.
So we will keep enduring to the end.

